  "detailed_description": "<h1>Just Updated</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2479810/extras/a832e2ad97d74cc9c045dd18e1e80796.poster.avif?t=1772807686\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2479810/extras/a832e2ad97d74cc9c045dd18e1e80796.webm?t=1772807686\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2479810/extras/a832e2ad97d74cc9c045dd18e1e80796.mp4?t=1772807686\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Patch 0.3.5.0 reflects over four months of daily development and fine-tuning, bringing numerous changes, including Unreal Engine 5.5 upgrade, Performance Enhancements, AI Aiming & Vulnerability Improvements, Recoil & Weapon Sway Overhaul, Shooting Sound Tweaks, and much more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into Gray Zone Warfare, and experience a much smoother and authentic open world.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Additions:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unreal Engine 5.5 Upgrade</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Performance Enhancements</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >AI Aiming & Vulnerability Improvements</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Weapon Sway Overhaul</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Recoil Overhaul</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shooting Sound Tweaks</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >FPV Movement Improvements</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >New Server Region - Mainland China</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Improved Death Screen</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Improved Bullet Penetration through skull and bones</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Balanced Rewards for Strike Missions</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Key drop frequency in Fort Narith fixed</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Improved scope visibility under specific weather conditions</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Updated the NVIDIA DLSS plugin to version 8.1.0</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Updated to AMD FSR 4</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More fixes & improvements. See the full Changelog on Steam News.</p></li></ul></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2479810/extras/55b9af672c0124e2347eed4cfd4b57a2.poster.avif?t=1772807686\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2479810/extras/55b9af672c0124e2347eed4cfd4b57a2.webm?t=1772807686\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2479810/extras/55b9af672c0124e2347eed4cfd4b57a2.mp4?t=1772807686\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2479810/extras/d0ae33972bc15b60b69dd7c52d2c84b9.poster.avif?t=1772807686\" width=780 height=700 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2479810/extras/d0ae33972bc15b60b69dd7c52d2c84b9.webm?t=1772807686\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2479810/extras/d0ae33972bc15b60b69dd7c52d2c84b9.mp4?t=1772807686\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2479810/extras/e8e560ae2fb1de3f7fa71e3aa4f229e5.poster.avif?t=1772807686\" width=780 height=700 ><source src=\"ht